---

## ✨ Features

- **Hero Section** — Eye-catching landing with a call-to-action to browse pets
- **Pet Adoption Cards** — Browsable cards showing each pet's name, age, gender, and breed
- **Gallery** — Image grid showcasing pets available for adoption
- **Our Services** — Overview of what the adoption center offers
- **About Us** — Mission and story of PetAdopt
- **Contact Form** — Message form with contact details
- **Responsive Navbar** — Mobile-friendly navigation with Bootstrap collapse
- **Footer** — Quick links and social media icons

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| HTML5 | Page structure and semantic markup |
| CSS3 | Custom styling and layout |
| Bootstrap 5.3 | Responsive grid, components, navbar |
| Bootstrap Icons | Social media and UI icons |

