## 🚀 Getting Started

No build tools or installations needed — just open the project in your browser.

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/rajpureaishwaryaadhik-star/portfolio.git

# 2. Open index.html in your browser
open index.html
```

Or simply double-click `index.html` to run it locally.

